      "id": "mem-MEMORY-critical-anti-patterns--verifi",
      "content": "### Drizzle chaining — SILENT BUG\n`.where(a).where(b)` — second replaces first. ALWAYS `.where(and(a, b))`.\nAlso in `paginateQuery` — pass `baseConditions` param, not pre-built query.\n\n### Multi-tenant leak\nEvery SQL needs `eq(table.providerId, providerId)`. Use cases need `providerId: string` (required). Post-fetch: `entity.providerId !== providerId → NotFoundError`.\n\n### Frontend FSD\n- page.tsx max 50 lines, ZERO inline components/functions\n- Every component = separate file (entities/ui/ or wi",
